data.description:
AMAZING VIP CUSTOM HOME ON OVER 3/4 AN ACRE WITH  PEBBLETEC POOL, RV PARKING, 3 CAR GARAGE, AND OVER $170K IN OPTIONS/UPGRADES! ATTENTION VA BUYERS - ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 4.5%! HOA ALLOWS DETACHED RV GARAGE IF BUYER WANTS TO BUILD! This spacious home boasts 15' coffered ceilings, 3 Bedrooms plus a Den, 2.5 Baths, Great Room/Kitchen open concept, Formal Dining, upgraded plank tile flooring, upgraded light fixtures, elevated quartz countertops, stone backsplash, upgraded cabinets, undermount sink, double ovens, built-in microwave with  air fryer, R/O system, undercabinet lighting, black stainless steel appliances, double doors at Master Bedroom,  barn door to Master Bath, huge walk-in shower with dual showerheads, programmable Wi-Fi thermostat, security camera system, epoxy garage flooring, water softener, garage cabinets, and the list goes on.
Your back yard oasis includes a huge, self-cleaning, Pebbletec pool, travertine deck, artificial turf, extended covered patio, travertine walkways, easy maintenance desert landscaping, RV parking, and elevated block fencing for extra privacy. The front yard includes a paver driveway to the RV gate, circular driveway, grand porch, paver walkways, and upgraded front door. Energy efficient home with solar panels, high efficiency 14 seer HVAC system, R-24 wall insulation system, foam & blown insulation, 2'x6' construction, and Low-E dual pane windows. Great location near Luke AFB and just minutes from schools, shopping, restaurants, Westgate Entertainment District, and the I-10/Loop 101 freeways. Must see!
